<section id="reference-hibernate_mapping-tree_view">
  <title>Tree view</title>
  <para>
    The Hibernate XML editor <guilabel>Tree</guilabel> view provides access to the elements of the mapping file in a structured way. Elements are presented in textboxes or mult-choice dropdown lists where appropriate to assist in editing the file.
  </para>
  <figure id="figure-reference-hibernate_mapping-tree_vieww_01">
    <title>Hibernate XML Editor - Tree View</title>
    <mediaobject>
      <imageobject>
        <imagedata fileref="images/image-hib-edit_mapping_file_02.png" format="PNG"/>
      </imageobject>
      <textobject>
        <para>Hibernate XML Editor - Tree View</para>
      </textobject>
    </mediaobject>
  </figure>
   <formalpara><title>Related material</title>
    <para>
      Further tasks and information relating to this editor are accessible from:  <xref linkend="document_navigation-hibernate_mapping"/>.
    </para>
  </formalpara> 
